==================================================
PHASE 2 – WALLS
==================================================
OBJECTIVE: Build strong exterior walls with interior reinforcement, spanning baseplate area.

APPROX WALL HEIGHT: ~40 bricks (≈15")

REQUIRED PARTS:
• 3004 – Brick 1×2 (x180)
• 3010 – Brick 1×4 (x80)
• 3008 – Brick 1×8 (x60)
• 3023 – Plate 1×2 (x220)

--------------------------------------------------
STEP-BY-STEP INSTRUCTIONS
--------------------------------------------------

STEP 1: ESTABLISH FIRST LAYER AROUND FRAME  
Use (12) Brick 1×8 (3008)  
- Begin along the edge of the Technic frame  
- Lay bricks in a full rectangular outline, flush with Technic brick ends  
- Ensure all bricks are fully seated on studs of the Technic base

STEP 2: INTERLOCK WITH SECOND LAYER  
Use mix of:
- (8) Brick 1×4 (3010)
- (10) Brick 1×2 (3004)

- Stagger all seams for interlock (like masonry)  
- Avoid vertical joints stacking directly over one another

STEP 3: REPEAT LAYERS TO HEIGHT 10  
- Continue alternating 1×2, 1×4, and 1×8 bricks  
- Every 4 layers, place a row of Plate 1×2 (3023) across the interior wall face  
  - Purpose: act as tension layers & connection plates  
  - Helps bind future sub-assemblies (tower, roof, etc.)

EXAMPLE PATTERN FOR EACH 4-LAYER MODULE:
- Layer 1: 1×8 perimeter
- Layer 2: 1×4 and 1×2 mix, offset
- Layer 3: repeat Layer 1
- Layer 4: 1×2 plates (horizontal), covering interior gaps

STEP 4: REPEAT MODULE UNTIL HEIGHT 40  
- You will build 10 total 4-layer modules  
- Total bricks used will approach:
  - ~60 1×8 bricks
  - ~80 1×4 bricks
  - ~180 1×2 bricks
  - ~220 1×2 plates

STEP 5: ADD STIFFENING BRICKS INSIDE CORNERS  
(Optional but recommended)  
- Insert 1×4 bricks inside all four corners every 6 bricks vertically  
- Purpose: increase torsional rigidity of the structure

FINAL CHECK:
✅ Walls rise to full height (~15")  
✅ All vertical seams staggered  
✅ Plates added every 4 layers  
✅ Connects flush with Technic frame base  
✅ Inside ready to receive Tower/Bridge assembly

==================================================
END OF PHASE 2 – WALLS COMPLETE
Next Phase: ROOF + DECK
==================================================
